=09=09=09=09Freeing  trade in the Americas=20
=09=09=09=09Protesters  captured much of the media attention at the Summit =
of the=20
Americas  in Quebec on April 20th-22nd. The leaders themselves were=20
undeterred.  They took an important step towards their goal: creating the=
=20
largest  free-trade area in the world.=20
